        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/b_buzzini/{size}/636_2.png",
        "created_at": "2026-03-12T00:24:25.877Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Oh\u2026I see now\u2026didn\u2019t know there was Les Champs Gains in both Puligny and Chassagne! Like Monty! That would be a cool side by side\u2026</p>\n<p>And\u2026doesn\u2019t appear they make these wines anymore? <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/william_kelley\">@William_Kelley</a></p>",
